N2  - Questionnaire data from 111 managers in a large utility firm showed significant positive relationships between supportiveness of the organizational climate in managers' immediate work groups and their assessment of MBO effectiveness. Climate-MBO effectiveness relationships were moderated by managers' need for independence and the type of work performed, but unaffected by organization level.
